item.description:
Starting near the Uncanoonuc Lake town beach we will hike to the top of South Uncanoonuc Mtn. (the one with all the communication towers on the top of it). 

Here is a link to a trail map.  Note that we are not starting this hike where it says you are here on the map but near Uncanoonuc Lake near the base of South Uncanoonuc Mtn.

 http://www.nhmountainhiking.com/hike/uncanoonuc/posted_map_big.jpg
item.how_to_find_us: Once on Mtn. Base Road take it 0.9 miles towards the end, turn right till you come to the town beach and park there.

group.name: Human Soles & Doggie Paws Hikers & Walkers of Manchester, NH
